paragraph.text:
the term
				Director means the Director of the Office of Management and
				Budget;

the term
				Inspector General has the meaning defined by section
				5(e)(1);

the term
				local government means the government of a political subdivision
				of a State;

clause.text:
the making of
				authorized payments or the prevention, identification, or recovery of improper
				payments;

subparagraph.text:
the term agency means an
				executive agency as that term is defined under 
                    section 102 of title 31;
